{"pageProps":{"eyebrow":"bpftime","page":{"layout":"document","title":"EIM: Example code","description":"See the source for this page to get example code for the EIM.","bodyHtml":"<p>See the source for this page to get example code for the EIM.</p>\n<h2 id=\"build-the-example\">build the example</h2>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">make</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<h2 id=\"see-the-types-defined-for-the-example\">See the types defined for the example</h2>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">$</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> bpftool</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> btf</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> dump</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> file</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> /home/yunwei37/bpftime-evaluation/interfeace/test.btf</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">[1] INT </span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\">'int'</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\"> size</span><span style=\"color:#F47067\">=</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\">4</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\"> bits_offset</span><span style=\"color:#F47067\">=</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\">0</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\"> nr_bits</span><span style=\"color:#F47067\">=</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\">32</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\"> encoding</span><span style=\"color:#F47067\">=</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\">SIGNED</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">[2] TYPEDEF </span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\">'size_t'</spa